SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = 'c397d14b9260cb0b4f94a1f665431b85e78d4ea6'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '2'

FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '1b5d52c8a10d35cfd8f49bf86d923ab33885cd4d'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '2'

FROM `users`
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'

FROM `users_groups`

SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '1f0e721cd2774d8ff0a2f0d0fa53db5a33c759d5'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

FROM `users_groups`

WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`

FROM `ci_sessions`

FROM `users`

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '6'
SELECT `id_question`, `motscles`, `statusStatistiques`, `statusParticulier`, `statusProfessionnel`
FROM `question`

WHERE `id_question` = '7'

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '1'

FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '0c174e4655f1893ec94aa49da953d092fab2c4cc'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`

FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '3'

FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '0c174e4655f1893ec94aa49da953d092fab2c4cc'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`

 LIMIT 1

FROM `question`

FROM `users`

FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'

FROM `users_groups`

WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '2'

SELECT GET_LOCK('0c174e4655f1893ec94aa49da953d092fab2c4cc', 300) AS ci_session_lock
SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '0c174e4655f1893ec94aa49da953d092fab2c4cc'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`

SELECT GET_LOCK('bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4', 300) AS ci_session_lock
SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = 'bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '2'

SELECT GET_LOCK('bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4', 300) AS ci_session_lock
SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = 'bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `id_question`, `libelle`, `motscles`, `statusGenerale`, `statusStatistiques`, `statusParticulier`, `statusProfessionnel`, `dateAjout`
FROM `question`
JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
SELECT *
FROM `reponses`
SELECT `id_question`, `motscles`, `statusStatistiques`, `statusParticulier`, `statusProfessionnel`
FROM `question`

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '1'

SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = 'bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = 'bf067305828cd760736d4ea89281f80e7e9a3ed4'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'

FROM `users_groups`

WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '2'

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '7'

WHERE `id` = '2683df66f3126dfe122f37bfab9895968a3c8ab9'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `id_question`, `libelle`, `motscles`, `statusGenerale`, `statusStatistiques`, `statusParticulier`, `statusProfessionnel`, `dateAjout`
FROM `question`
JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
SELECT *
FROM `reponses`

JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
WHERE `id_question` = '7'

FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '7895900112eefb20d9cea51d468f4510c9875244'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1

FROM `client`

SELECT GET_LOCK('7895900112eefb20d9cea51d468f4510c9875244', 300) AS ci_session_lock
SELECT `data`
FROM `ci_sessions`
WHERE `id` = '7895900112eefb20d9cea51d468f4510c9875244'
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
WHERE `users`.`id` = '1'
ORDER BY `users`.`id` DESC
 LIMIT 1
SELECT `id_question`, `libelle`, `motscles`, `statusGenerale`, `statusStatistiques`, `statusParticulier`, `statusProfessionnel`, `dateAjout`
FROM `question`
JOIN `categorie` ON `categorie`.`id` = `question`.`keywordId`
SELECT `users`.*, `users`.`id` as `id`, `users`.`id` as `user_id`
FROM `users`
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '1'
SELECT `users_groups`.`group_id` as `id`, `groups`.`name`, `groups`.`description`
FROM `users_groups`
JOIN `groups` ON `users_groups`.`group_id`=`groups`.`id`
WHERE `users_groups`.`user_id` = '2'
